---
import Link from "../atoms/Link.astro";
import StoryImage from "../molecules/StoryImage.astro";
---

<header class="flow">
  <div>
    <ul role="list">
      <li>
        <Link href="/" text="Finans" classes="tag" />
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h1>
      Ny konkursbølge under oppseiling: – Nå blir det verre
    </h1>
    <h2>
      Konkurstallene stiger mot nye høyder. Så langt i år er antall konkurser innen detaljhandel og hotell/restaurant blitt mer enn doblet sammenlignet med i fjor.
    </h2>
  </div>
  <StoryImage />
</header>

<style>
  header {
    align-items: start;
    background-color: var(--hero-bkg, hsl(0 0% 100%));
    color: var(--hero-text-clr, currentColor);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-areas: "a" "b";
    padding-block-start: var(--hero-top-space, 1.75rem);
  }

  ul[role="list"] {
    inline-size: min(
      var(--body-col-width),
      100vw - calc(var(--site-padding) * 2)
    );
    margin-inline: auto;
    list-style-type: none;
    margin-block-end: 1.5rem;
    padding-inline-start: 0;
  }

  div {
    background-color: var(--hero-text-bkg, hsl(0 0% 100%));
    /* color: currentColor; */
    display: grid;
    grid-area: var(--hero-text, a);
    padding-block-start: var(--hero-text-space, 1.75rem);
    row-gap: 0.5rem;

    & > * {
      inline-size: min(
        var(--body-col-width),
        100vw - calc(var(--site-padding) * 2)
      );
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--hero-font, "SmBold23", sans-serif);
    font-size: var(--hero-font-size, 2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    padding-block-start: 1rem;
  }
</style>
